Class GeoLocation

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.denishamann.guesstimate.model.GeoLocation

  • public class GeoLocation
extends java.lang.Object
    a analog implementation of the GeoPoint, but reduced to our usecase. Needed for osmdroid independent Testing outside of the android framework. Basic idea is to have a higher modularity and being less depending on osmdroid.
    Author:
    denis
